Files in this directory are handled by the OpenEngSB deployer services.
These services listen for new/changed/deleted files and automatically
update the corresponding configuration in OpenEngSB.

For detailed information please check the manual.

Supported file types
--------------------
.connector (property file) - Connector instance configuration
.context - Context configuration
.rf - Workflow-process files
.rule - Rule definitions
.function - Function definitions
.import - list of imports for drools
.globals - list of drools globals
.transformation - Transformation description definitions

